    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp via individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been overhauled and the rod bearings replaced with VAC coated bearings for longevity. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a crucial prophylactic measure. Suspension dynamics are preserved with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth with zero oxidation. A true driver's machine with a documented service history that validates its mechanical integrity.",
