      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that can only be described as a 'time capsule.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections of any kind. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is pristine and remains smoke-free and pet-free. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, creasing, or fading, and the carpets have been protected by original factory mats since day one. All technological features, including the navigation suite and driver-assistance systems, operate exactly as they did the day the car left the showroom floor. Mechanically, the vehicle is indistinguishable from new, with a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and all owner's manuals. For the buyer seeking perfection without compromise, this is the one.",
